{"tid":703790,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔計入球數齋計入球質素，琴晚 C 朗 >>>>> 哥斯達","createTime":"2018-06-16T02:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T02:50:33.000Z","uid":46849,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40a0acf3c309f77729fee8060c748b29fd5280b4","tid":703790,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"如果你 SICK 波<br />\n<br />\n就知C朗好過哥斯達多多聲啦<br />\n<br />\n哥斯達果兩球，第一球打完人扮冇事，見人訓係度冇D 風度繼續攻<br />\n<br />\n第二球 Tap-in，我阿婆都入到啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC 朗入三球數目小事，但第一球單騎搏到十二碼，仲冷靜入埋開齋，不負球玉之名<br />\n<br />\n第二球勁射，接到都入，咁唔叫勁？<br />\n<br />\n第三球唔駛講啦，又係球玉，衝力射球曲墜入網，仲想點？"},{"pid":"e69373938762fcd8145e8e08411610b3806ea384","tid":703790,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"齋負評又不敢留言<br />\n<br />\n係咩心態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64af856b67a94fce75481a1d4b80eadc30d7a75","tid":703790,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"一個 tap in<br />\n<br />\n一個接到都入<br />\n<br />\n邊個勁d 唔駛講下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be77ead526b442aed7840a09c509a26aab63e7e","tid":703790,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64af856b67a94fce75481a1d4b80eadc30d7a75","tid":703790,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"一個 tap in<br />\n<br />\n一個接到都入<br />\n<br />\n邊個勁d 唔駛講下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}